3.14.4
======
I am working on the new document: https://avimitin.github.io/nvim.
The basic keymap section is finished now.

Breaking Chnages:
----------------
* keymap: add ctrl as prefix key when resize (See commit `b545fafe <|CommitPrefix|b545fafe>`_)
* keymap: use arrow key to navigate between windows (See commit `70576e9d <|CommitPrefix|70576e9d>`_)
* keymap: delete the duplicate new tab keymap, only `<C-t> n` is kept (See commit `6369ca63 <|CommitPrefix|6369ca63>`_)
* keymap: set `gf` to buffer format, set `gq` to set_loclist, set `gt` to...
  ...type_definition (See commit 346bfe58 and 3111d496)

Features:
---------
* plugin: add plugin vim-startuptime, you can see the startuptime graph by...
  ...command `:StartupTime` (See commit `7018a3e3 <|CommitPrefix|7018a3e3>`_)
* command: add `Cmt` to make a commit, add `Psh` to push changes. (See commit `8b9d959a <|CommitPrefix|8b9d959a>`_)
* plugin: add new plugin FixCursorHold.nvim to fix the laggy event (See commit `0164a37d <|CommitPrefix|0164a37d>`_)


